WEBVTT

00:06:58.267 --> 00:07:00.080
Grade school was spectacular for me.

00:07:00.104 --> 00:07:02.048
It was, really, a wonderful experience.

00:07:02.072 --> 00:07:05.026
(Laughter)

00:07:05.420 --> 00:07:07.262
But you might be saying to yourselves,

00:07:07.286 --> 00:07:10.634
You know, all of these weapons
in war zones -- they're not a cause,

00:07:10.658 --> 00:07:13.080
but an effect of the violence
that plagues them

00:07:13.104 --> 00:07:14.588
each and every single day.

00:07:14.612 --> 00:07:16.795
You know, places like Iraq
and Afghanistan,

00:07:16.819 --> 00:07:20.233
where they need these weapons
to be able to maintain law and order,

00:07:20.257 --> 00:07:23.878
promote peace and security,
to combat terror groups --

00:07:23.902 --> 00:07:26.397
surely this is a good thing.

00:07:26.773 --> 00:07:29.461
Let's take a look at that assumption
for just one moment,

00:07:29.485 --> 00:07:33.271
because you see there has been
a boom in the small-arms trade